contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.communi.CommunityGroupContentDescription:
Do you work with Kentico and want to stay informed of the latest developments and innovative solutions by fellow Kentico users? Have you recently worked on an interesting project and would you like to share this knowledge with the community? Attend for a fun afternoon with other Kentico enthusiasts.

The Kentico User Group meetings are always free of charge and are made possible by voluntary contribution from Kentico partners.
